Obsidian Plume (obsidian-theme-plume)
-------------------------------------

This Obsidian plugin was created by porting concepts, markup conventions, styles,
and implementation patterns from VuePress Theme Plume to Obsidian. Much of the
migration was performed with AI-assisted development tools (e.g. Cursor).

This repository is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or maintained by the
vuepress-theme-plume authors. It is an independent community port for Obsidian.

